root: ^Floating several feet above the bed, you see a girl with a mane of red hair, short faun-like horns and skin that tapers into fuzzy brown fur.
^She does not have human feet, but instead hooves slightly darker than the fur on her legs.
^Her face is contorted not in pain but as if she is focusing on something, her fists clenched.
^You hear that voice in your head again.
